Patch: Add GGML_TYPE_F8_E4M3FN to ggml (type id 40)
Applies to: llama.cpp b8665 (commit 9c69907) — tested April 2026
Files modified:
  ggml/include/ggml.h
  ggml/src/ggml-cpu/ggml-quants.h
  ggml/src/ggml-cpu/ggml-quants.c
  gguf-py/gguf/constants.py

FP8 overflow fix (critical): exp8 overflow boundary is > 15, not >= 15.
  E4M3FN allows exp=15 as a valid normal (e.g. 256.0 = exp8=15, mant=0).
  Only exp=15 + mant=7 is NaN. Previous version encoded 256..447 as 448.

Apply: git apply src/ggml_fp8.patch
Build: cmake --build build --config Release -j

